33415|"GESCHWITZ. How the attendants in the hospital got out of her way"|FALSE
33415|"yesterday! That was a refreshing sight. The garden was still as the"|FALSE
33415|"grave: in the loveliest noon sunlight the convalescents didn't"|FALSE
33415|"venture out of doors. Away back by the contagious ward she stepped"|FALSE
